title: Wholesale Price of Rayon Yarn for New York, NY
notes:
Data Refers To Rayon Yarn: "150 Denier, First Quality, Domestic, Minimum Filament, Bright Luster, Viscose Process Skeins At New York City -- Averages Of Quotations For All Working Days In The Month." Source: Textile Economics Bureau, Inc., "Rayon Organon", Special Supplements, January 21, 1941, Pp. 24-25; January 21, 1944, P. 25; July 1944 Issue.
